item.title: Okay.thats one problem solved.how about this? :)
item.dc:creator: @xx_qwertyuiop_xx xx qwertyuiop xx
item.description:
@xx_qwertyuiop_xx wrote:

The variable hasn’t declared.

E.X: If I made a class like this:

public class lol
{
public static void main(String args[])
{
l0lwut = 2;
}
}

I would get an unfound variable error which can easily be solved by declaring the variable.

public class lol
{
public static void main(String args[])
{
public int l0lwut;
l0lwut = 2;
}
}
